  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3000 liters of fuel seized from Vavuniya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nelukkulama Police have arrested a businessman with 3000 liters of illegally collected diesel at a construction site in the Veppamkulama area in Vavuniya.",
        "He said that the suspect was arrested in a raid carried out on a tip-off received by the police regarding a businessman who was collecting diesel to sell at a higher price.",
        "The suspect had hidden 15 barrels of illegally stockpiled diesel in the warehouse of his business premises, police said.",
        "Police said they had received information that a black market businessman in the area was selling diesel for between 600 and 800 rupees a liter and that investigations were underway to arrest them."
      ],
